high_descs: Wash the soap in the sink.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank in front of and to the left of the toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Pick up the soap in the tub.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Wet the soap with water in the sink.
Bring the soap to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the bath tub.
Pick up the pink bar soap inside the tub.
Place the soap inside the sink, rinse it, and pick it up.
Turn around and walk towards the toilet.
Place the soap on the toilet basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bar soap on the toilet basin.
